{
  "texts": [
    "Mohseni et al.",
    "1 and Wang et al.",
    "39 demonstrated that by minimizing the system's energy expressed by the Hamiltonian, the system's state naturally evolves towards the ground state, effectively solving the COP.",
    "Analyzing the system's energy while considering its oscillatory nature through the Kuramoto model under specific conditions shows that the ONN minimizes a Lyapunov equation 23, 39, 41.",
    "When the states are simplified to a binary form, this equation is equivalent to the Ising Hamiltonian, ensuring the system evolves to a lower and stable energy state 39, 41."
  ]
}